data.description: This home is ready for your family. This home  has an Open Concept Floor Plan Home with a lot of Stylish Upgrades!! As you walk in the front door you will see tile throughout the foyer, running to the spacious kitchen and hallways. Granite countertops in the bathrooms and Kitchen. Whirlpool Stainless Steel Appliances, Microwave, stove, Oversized Cafe/Dining Room Area with Modern Chandelier, spacious Gathering Room that opens to the 12x9 Covered Lanai.  Large owners Suite with an Oversized Walk-In Closet. Stone Gray Cabinets with Dual Granite sink Countertop, Walk-In Shower with Frameless Glass. Comfort Height Elongated Commode in bathrooms, Spacious Flex/Den with nicely designed french doors for Privacy. This room can also be for Home Office, Fitness Room or Extra Bedroom, Large Laundry Great Mud Room Area Off Garage, 2" Faux Wood Blinds Throughout Home, upgraded Hypoallergenic carpet in rooms, Garage Keyless Entry, In ceiling speaker wires, 42" wiring panel, Access point pre-wire. This community comes with a large Community Pool & Playground! Great Location - Close Proximity to Major Highways FL-429 & FL-414, Schools, Restaurants & Shopping. COME MUST SEE WHILES IT'S STILL AVAIABLE!!
